                                 Welcome to the Forecast Systems Laboratory!

   Visitor and Information Services supports the Forecast Systems
   Laboratory by providing assistance in arranging tours or visits and in
   scheduling appropriate FSL staff in order to meet visitors' needs.
   These services are provided for schools, government officials, the
   private sector and general public, and foreign countries.

   If you:
     * are a school group (3rd grade and up) and have just completed a
       weather unit,
     * have need for information about weather related phenomena,
     * work in the meteorological field, or
     * are simply a weather enthusiast and interested in state-of-the-art
       technology...
        YOU may want to visit FSL.

